last_episode_to_air.overview: Roadkill Nights powered by Dodge in Pontiac, Michigan, is arguably one of the best automotive events in the country.

name: The House of Muscle
overview: Take a look inside the world's obsession with the muscle car. From home-built rat-rods to priceless rolling works of art, host Mike Musto not only profiles the cars and their place in history, but then takes these amazing machines out for a flat-out, no-holds-barred test drive.
